{"tid":1036198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強国玻璃心又碎】全球最大六四紀念碑　加州落成高6.4米","createTime":"2019-02-25T05:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T05:16:24.000Z","uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"880dc13cbe8923021cd306befbb64405d7b6fd89","tid":1036198,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"全球最大六四紀念碑 加州落成高6.4米<br />\n<br />\n六四事件30周年將至，全球最大的六四事件紀念碑於上周六（23日）於美國加州落成，吸引200多人出席揭幕儀式。<br />\n<br />\n紀念碑主體由阿拉伯數字「64」所組成，該碑目前坐落於連接洛杉磯和拉斯維加斯的15號州際公路旁。創作者陳維明向境外媒體表示，早前同幾名友人於美國買下這塊佔地14.5萬平方米的土地，欲想此地打造成民主、自由、人權為主題的「自由雕塑公園」。<br />\n<br />\n陳稱，紀念碑主體的高度及總高度分別為6.4米及8.9米，距離北京的距離及角度均與「64」有關，含紀念當年六四事件的意義。他稱，不想遺忘當年事件，又形容「是中國人心中的傷痛」。"},{"pid":"95b1cdf23bff97f7e996e1b3ba94782ec68de9a8","tid":1036198,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190224/photo/bkn-20190224190140743-0224_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190224212012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190224190140743-0224_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190224212012&h=e8724cf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54656a01838cd332658d7499878a0ac0637eea33","tid":1036198,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190224/mobile/bkn-20190224190140743-0224_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190224%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190224190140743-0224_00972_001.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8dekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=bc2140bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190224/mobile/bkn-20190224190140743-0224_00972_001.html</a>"}]}